{"TopicId":179796,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"Pilot deufrai : introduction","CreatedByName":"deufrai","CreatedById":193221,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T09:16:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"deufrai","CreatedById":193221,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T09:16:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi there\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA quick introduction after less than 10 hours into stock career mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrench guy, starting to grow grey hair, amateur astronomer and astrophotography enthusiast, I stumbled into KSP just a few days ago and already got to learn so much about ships and orbital mechanics. Thanks, among others, to many good YT videos.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGamewise, I achieved my first Mun flyby with maneuver nodes but without any \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, as I decided to send a scientist up there to boost my tech tree progression.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis \u0027Welcome Aboard\u0022 forum description states that this is the right place to get quick tips, so here I go \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThe Pilot I used to fly (\u003C/span\u003Ejebediah) died after having achieved Kerbin orbit, put the Sputnik in high Kerbin orbit and also gained \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E ability \u002B prograde \u002B retrograde. He then resurrected according to my \u0027Normal\u0027 difficulty set level and settings. But those 3 abilities are gone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is the best way to regain those abilities ? I assume redoing what he already achieved won\u0027t do the job and that I\u0027m better off hiring a new pilot and make him gain those abilities quickly before aiming to further targets. Is that assumption correct ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, clear skies to all \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T11:48:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193221-deufrai/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022193221\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193221-deufrai/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@deufrai\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny kerbal, Jeb included, becomes level 1 on first orbit - regardless if they have been resurrected.\u00A0 Experience makes all classes better at their jobs.\u00A0 There is a rundown on the wiki that explains the requirements and abilities: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Experience\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Experience\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"deufrai","CreatedById":193221,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T13:00:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the reply. I did acutally see the wiki page you mentionned.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy interrogation is : as Jeb gained level 1 on his firt orbit before he died, will he gain level 1 again if I put him as Pilot of a ship I send in orbit ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T14:04:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223487099\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179796\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221542200415\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193221\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022deufrai\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, deufrai said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwill he gain level 1 again if I put him as Pilot of a ship I send in orbit ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup, he should do \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"deufrai","CreatedById":193221,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T14:12:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223487117\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179796\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221542204258\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup, he should do \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi and thanks. I\u0027ll test this and report so we can convert this \u0027should\u0027 into a \u0022must\u0022 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"deufrai","CreatedById":193221,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T18:04:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi again,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust did an orbit with resurrected Jeb, and he got his first star back. Thanks for the info / tip \u003Cspan\u003E:)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-14T23:29:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst of all, welcome to the forums! If you want to, you can share your KSP beginner\u0027s story in this thread:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5874473638\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/179199-your-first-hours-in-ksp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope you enjoy all that the forum has to offer, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193221-deufrai/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022193221\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193221-deufrai/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@deufrai\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-15T23:29:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBienvenu! You surely have many exciting adventures ahead of you in this game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Adstri","CreatedById":174024,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-16T01:26:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBonjour!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe actually have an astrophotography thread here:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6370848742\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/148056-the-astro-imaging-thread/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:228px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe that\u0027s something you\u0027d like to check out?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBienvenue sur \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003Eles\u003C/abbr\u003E forums! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}